								<div class="box-white">
									<h2 class=vol-title">Health Through New Thought and Fasting </h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-3-4-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="Health Through New Thought and Fasting " alt="Health Through New Thought and Fasting " height="235" width="300"/>
									<p class="regular">Food is nourishment and necessary to sustain Life, but the REAL FUEL that our bodies need is first and foremost sourced from the Mind. More food does not lead to more energy; many already understand this to be true. Why, then, do so many struggle with weight loss and maintaining healthy eating habits?</p>
									<p class="regular">In &ldquo;Health Through New Thought and Fasting,&rdquo; Wattles teaches his Scientific, step-by-step method for proper Nutrition, Sleep and Living Habits &mdash; in conjunction with Constructive Thought, Speech and Action &mdash; to attain a rigorous, balanced and HEALTHY Life! Learn to distinguish between &ldquo;hunger&rdquo; &mdash; your body&rsquo;s TRUE need for fuel &mdash; and &ldquo;appetite&rdquo; &mdash; your conditioned, habit patterns to eat when it is not necessary! Learn HOW to use YOUR Mind to facilitate and increase efficiency in eating, digestion and assimilation of Food.&nbsp; And, by learning and practicing proper Sleep methods, you will develop the POWER of renewing, re-energizing and revitalizing YOUR Subconscious Mind, thereby realizing NEW sources of energy to POWER YOUR LIFE!</p>
									<p class="regular">Using the Scientific Methods of &ldquo;Health Through New Thought and Fasting,&rdquo; YOU can learn HOW to MASTER YOUR HEALTH!&nbsp; As the old adage says, &ldquo;He who has his health, has everything!&rdquo;</p>							

									<div id="divider"> 
										<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/divider.png" /> 
									</div><!-- #divider close -->	
									
									<ul class="tick">
										<li>Commentary by Elizabeth Towne.</li>
										<li>The &ldquo;Source of Work Power&rdquo; and its relationship with diet and sleep.&nbsp; How to increase Your Work Power for a more energetic, stronger and more healthful Life.</li>
										<li>Why the concept of &ldquo;food is fuel&rdquo; is not accurate and how You REALLY generate Work Power.</li>
										<li>How Your Mind &mdash; and not necessarily the food You eat &mdash; provides Instant Energy and fuels Your Body.</li>
										<li>The &ldquo;No Breakfast Plan&rdquo; &mdash; what it is and how it can be used to generate physical vigor and vitality and strong mental acuity.</li>
										<li>Why over-eating leads to poor health, a lower metabolism, and more sleep.</li>
										<li>What and how to properly eat when sick in order to regain Health and strength quickly.</li>
										<li>Sleep &mdash; proper Sleep and how vital energy is renewed in Sleep.</li>
										<li>Why proper Sleep is necessary for promoting the inflow of Energy and Life Force.</li>
										<li>How the Subconscious Mind works during proper Sleep to repair, renew and revitalize the Body &mdash; from a systemic to a cellular level.</li>
										<li>How Your Healing Powers, stored in the Mind, are activated and work during proper Sleep.</li>
										<li>How to Use Sleep &mdash; with proper Breathing &mdash; to attain and maintain perfect Health.</li>
										<li>Pure air vs. stagnant air &mdash; why pure air is critically important to Your Health.</li>
										<li>Scientific Living and Healing &mdash; the use of Scientific Methods to overcome sickness and foster vigorous Health.</li>
										<li>How to &ldquo;clean&rdquo; Your circulatory system through proper eating habits.</li>
										<li>Proper and rational fasting to cleanse the Body of impurities.</li>
										<li>How to avoid &ldquo;germ diseases&rdquo; through proper eating, breathing and Sleep.</li>
										<li>Understanding that You are a Spiritual Being and maintaining Spiritual Health leads to Mental, Intellectual and Physical Health.</li>
										<li>&ldquo;Mind Cures&rdquo; &mdash; how to use the Mind to cure sickness, ailments and disease and overcome poor Physical Health.</li>
										<li>How the Brain acts through every organ, organ system and cell in the Body.&nbsp; As such, by using the Brain, You may affect every organ, organ system and cell in the Body.</li>
										<li>Exercise &mdash; what you REALLY need to know about Exercise and its impact on Your Body and Your Health.</li>
										<li>&ldquo;Nature and Development of the Will&rdquo; &mdash; learn why Nature&rsquo;s Laws are essential to understanding good Health.</li>
										<li>The &ldquo;Power of the Will&rdquo; in curing sickness and disease and overcoming poor Health to attain strength, vigor and good Health.</li>
										<li>The Power of Silence in Development of the Will and how to use it for good Health.</li>
										<li>Powerful Prayers and Affirmations to generate strong, vigorous Health &mdash; in Body, Mind and Spirit.</li>
										<li>How to create Greater Life within for a fuller expression in the external world.</li>
										<li>The Life Force of God &mdash; Understand how It lives in You and how to unite with It for a fuller, healthier Life.</li>
									</ul>

