								<div class="box-white">
									<h2 class=vol-title">Scientific Marriage</h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-3-5-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="Scientific Marriage" alt="Scientific Marriage" height="235" width="300"/>	<p class="regular">Most would agree that the Marital Relationship &mdash; Marriage &mdash; is one of Life&rsquo;s most common, but most complex relationships.&nbsp; It can be an amazing, beautiful and life-long experience &mdash; or it can be tragic.&nbsp; Why is it that some Marriages Succeed so well, while others end in emotional destruction and total failure?</p>
									<p class="regular">There is a Scientific Method to Marriage, and in &ldquo;Scientific Marriage,&rdquo; Master Wattles explains how to apply Scientific Principles to the Marital Relationship.</p>
									<p class="regular">Understanding that it is nature&rsquo;s will that reproduce, it is critically important to understand the relationship between sex and love and its impact on human relationships. Further, learning to differentiate between the different &ldquo;kinds&rdquo; of marriage (the various underlying reasons as to WHY we marry), can help avoid a marriage doomed from the start or even turn a marriage that is headed in the wrong direction.</p>
									<p class="regular">The Mind is our most POWERFUL God-given tool.&nbsp; By using it Scientifically in all aspects of our Lives &mdash; including Marriage &mdash; YOU can achieve a richer, more fulfilling and ABUNDANT LIFE!</p>

